;; Focus: core CS concepts across substrates:
;;   - Algorithms, programs, data structures, machine models
;;   - Complexity, computability, languages and semantics
;;   - Software systems, OS, concurrency, networking, databases
;;   - Security, verification, debugging, and CS-style reasoning
